    {
      "id": "PopularPost277756",
      "post_content": "This is a definite 4 out of 5, but the art work sucks. Definitely some of the worst art in the game. This cards deserves art like that of obsidian fireheart. The 3/1's need something to beef up their toughness though, but definitely an awesome way to create unexpected blockers. if you could make him indestructible and have mogg maniac out and cast blashemous act you could very quickly end a game. Vigor is the best incarnation to me but this card is a lot of fun.",
